True Blood follows a serialized format , with every episode ending on a cliffhanger that leads directly into the next .
A total of 80 episodes of True Blood were broadcast over seven seasons .
True Blood is an American television drama series created by Alan Ball and based on The Southern Vampire Mysteries  (  also known as The Sookie Stackhouse novels  )  by Charlaine Harris .
